svg.title: Effects and Benefits of Christian Baptism (Catholic Teaching)

g.text: Effects and Benefits of Christian Baptism (Catholic Teaching)
Form: "I baptize you in the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Spirit"
Extraordinary - Any person with proper intent
Description: Divine life infused into the soul
Description: Soul becomes a temple of the Holy Spirit
Description: Becomes member of God's family
Description: Enters the Body of Christ
and gains membership in the Church
